{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-lecture-template-tsx","path":"/lecture/프론트엔드 테스트/2024-01-21-시각적-회귀-테스트/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"0-들어가며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#0-%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\"0 들어가며 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>0. 들어가며</h2>\n<p>시각적 회귀 테스트의 정의와 <code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code>을 이용한 시각적 회귀 테스트 방법에 대하여 정리</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-시각적-회귀-테스트란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EC%8B%9C%EA%B0%81%EC%A0%81-%ED%9A%8C%EA%B7%80-%ED%85%8C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"1 시각적 회귀 테스트란 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 시각적 회귀 테스트란?</h2>\n<p>기존의 스냅샷 테스트에서 스냅샷이 문자열이 아닌 이미지로 저장되어 테스트를 진행하는 방법<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code>과 같은 도구를 사용하면 다음과 같은 장점이 있다</p>\n<ol>\n<li>일관된 환경에서 스냅샷을 찍을 수 있음</li>\n<li>AI 기반 비교 알고리즘으로 사용자 관점에서의 변경 사항을 찾아줌</li>\n<li>브라우저 마다 다른 렌더링 결과를 확인할 수 있음</li>\n<li>수정사항에 따른 히스토리를 확인할 수 있음</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"2-chromatic-시작하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-chromatic-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"2 chromatic 시작하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Chromatic 시작하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-storybook-연동\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-storybook-%EC%97%B0%EB%8F%99\" aria-label=\"1 storybook 연동 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(1) Storybook 연동</h3>\n<p>먼저 <code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code> 페이지에서 로그인 이후 <code class=\"language-text\">GitHub</code> 프로젝트와 연동, 제공해주는 명령어를 작성한다.<br>\n이러면 <code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code>에서 <code class=\"language-text\">Storybook</code>의 스토리를 기반으로 하여 기본적인 스냅샷이 저장되고, 이후 변경사항이 발생하면 <code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code>에서 변경사항을 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-커밋-후-스냅샷-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%BB%A4%EB%B0%8B-%ED%9B%84-%EC%8A%A4%EB%83%85%EC%83%B7-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"2 커밋 후 스냅샷 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(2) 커밋 후 스냅샷 확인</h3>\n<p>변경사항이 발생하고 커밋하고 <code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code> 배포 명령어를 진행하면 나에게 제공된 <code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code> 페이지에서 변경사항을 확인할 수 있다.<br>\n이때 <code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code> 배포 명령어는 내부적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">Storybook</code>을 빌드, 스냅샷을 찍고 <code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code> 페이지에 업로드하는 과정을 거친다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-chromatic-ci\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-chromatic-ci\" aria-label=\"3 chromatic ci permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Chromatic CI</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-pr-생성시-chromatic-실행\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-pr-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%EC%8B%9C-chromatic-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-label=\"1 pr 생성시 chromatic 실행 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(1) PR 생성시 Chromatic 실행</h3>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"43122160938523790000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`# .github/workflows/chromatic.yml\r\nname: 'chromatic test'\r\non: pull_request\r\njobs:\r\n  chromatic-deployment:\r\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\r\n    steps:\r\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v3\r\n        with:\r\n          fetch-depth: 0\r\n      - uses: actions/setup-node@v3\r\n        with:\r\n          node-version: 19\r\n      - name: Install dependencies\r\n        run: npm ci\r\n      - name: Publish to Chromatic\r\n        uses: chromaui/action@v1\r\n        with:\r\n          projectToken: \\${{ secrets.CHROMATIC_PROJECT_TOKEN }} # https://www.chromatic.com/docs/github-actions/\r\n          onlyChanged: true # https://www.chromatic.com/docs/turbosnap/#turbosnap`, `43122160938523790000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yml\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><code class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token comment\"># .github/workflows/chromatic.yml</span>\r\n<spa