ses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> chromaui/action@v1\r\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">with</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\r\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">projectToken</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.CHROMATIC_PROJECT_TOKEN <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># https://www.chromatic.com/docs/github-actions/</span>\r\n          <span class=\"token key atrule\">onlyChanged</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean important\">true</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># https://www.chromatic.com/docs/turbosnap/#turbosnap</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-pr-생성-및-ui-변경-시\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-pr-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%8F-ui-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD-%EC%8B%9C\" aria-label=\"2 pr 생성 및 ui 변경 시 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(2) PR 생성 및 UI 변경 시</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/Jeongseulho/Jeongseulho/assets/110578739/fa3b46d8-1477-408c-9fdf-93234e7438b2\" alt=\"image\">\r\n<code class=\"language-text\">UI Tests:</code>의 Details를 클릭하면 <code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code> 페이지로 이동하여 변경사항을 확인할 수 있고 스냅샷을 변경할지 여부를 결정<br>\n팀원의 PR를 확인할 때도 <code class=\"language-text\">UI Review:</code>의 Details을 클릭하여 <code class=\"language-text\">Chromatic</code> 페이지로 이동하여 변경사항을 확인하고 PR을 수락할지 여부를 결정</